T1  - Taxation and Corporate Pension Policy
AU  - TEPPER, IRWIN
Y1  - 1981/03/01
PY  - 1981
DA  - 1981/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1981.tb03530.x
